hi! Blue guifg=#00C0FF guibg=NONE guisp=NONE gui=NONE ctermfg=69 ctermbg=NONE cterm=NONE
hi! NeonGreen guifg=#00FF00 guibg=NONE guisp=NONE gui=NONE ctermfg=76 ctermbg=NONE cterm=NONE
